Task 1: Create IAM Users with Role-Based Access
🎯 Scenario

Company has:

Admin
Developer
Read-only user
🛠️ Steps
Go to IAM → Users → Create User
Create users:
admin-user
dev-user
viewer-user
Assign permissions:
Admin → AdministratorAccess
Dev → AmazonEC2FullAccess
Viewer → ReadOnlyAccess
📚 What You Learn
Role-based access control (RBAC)
Least privilege principle
